Package net.akami.mask.merge

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FairMerge<T,PROP extends FairOverallMergeProperty<T>>
    A merge producing a result of the same type as the input
    Merge<P,R,PROP extends OverallMergeProperty<P,R>>
    A behavior that takes two entries of the same type, and outputs a result that may or may not be of the same type.
    SequencedMerge<T>
    A merge concerning sequences of elements.
    SinglePropertySequencedMerge<T>
    A simple wrapper for SequencedMerges that only have one ElementSequencedMergeProperty.
